Because God so loved the world, he sent his only begotten son, Jesus Christ to pay the penalty with his blood. The only perfect and sinless man died in the cross, was buried and resurrected 3 days later defeating Satan and death. Surrender to Jesus and tell him you're sorry for sinning against Him and that you're ready to surrender your life to him and you will not perish but have everlasting life.
